      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-14">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay: 0;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#7C3AED]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><i class="fas fa-tags text-[#7C3AED] text-lg"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">최저가 보장</h3>
          <p class="text-[12px] text-[#111827]/40 mt-2">타사 대비 최저가 보장. 차액 200% 환불</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay: 1;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#7C3AED]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><i class="fas fa-shipping-fast text-[#7C3AED] text-lg"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">당일 배송</h3>
          <p class="text-[12px] text-[#111827]/40 mt-2">오후 2시 이전 주문 시 당일 출고</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay: 2;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#7C3AED]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><i class="fas fa-exchange-alt text-[#7C3AED] text-lg"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">30일 무료 반품</h3>
          <p class="text-[12px] text-[#111827]/40 mt-2">마음에 들지 않으면 무조건 환불</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay: 3;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#7C3AED]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><i class="fas fa-headset text-[#7C3AED] text-lg"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">24시간 고객센터</h3>
          <p class="text-[12px] text-[#111827]/40 mt-2">채팅, 전화, 이메일 상시 운영</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== Recommended Products ========== -->
  <section id="products" class="py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-14">
        <div>
          <span class="inline-block rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] font-bold bg-[#7C3AED]/5 text-[#7C3AED] reveal" style="--delay: 0;">추천</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-snug mt-4 font-dm reveal" style="--delay: 1;">추천 상품</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[#7C3AED] reveal" style="--delay: 2;">전체 보기 <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-[9px]"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6">
        <div class="product-card bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-[#7C3AED]/5 reveal" style="--delay: 0;">
          <div class="overflow-hidden bg-[#F3F4F6] relative">
