          <p class="text-[11px] text-[#111827]/30 mt-1">1,200+ 상품</p>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="category-card bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center border border-[#7C3AED]/5 reveal" style="--delay: 4;">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#7C3AED]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"><i class="fas fa-utensils text-[#7C3AED] text-xl"></i></div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-sm">식품</p>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-[#111827]/30 mt-1">800+ 상품</p>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="category-card bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center border border-[#7C3AED]/5 reveal" style="--delay: 5;">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#7C3AED]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"><i class="fas fa-running text-[#7C3AED] text-xl"></i></div>
